{"tid":2245601,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒：【就PSN使用者條款加入國安法相關條文去信SONY】","createTime":"2020-10-16T10:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T11:22:53.000Z","uid":294108,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"30c33b23d4b50c01f0530838d6090a46abe52313","tid":2245601,"uid":294108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bt53yrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBt53yrc.jpg&h=384b1fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【就PSN使用者條款加入國安法相關條文去信SONY】<br />\n<br />\n致索尼互動娛樂香港有限公司<br />\n<br />\n有關PSN使用者條款加入國安法相關條文的詢問<br />\n<br />\n有見近日有用戶表示，Sony在PSN的使用者條款中加入不少有關中國國安法的條款，雖然Playstation表示暫時條款只適用於居任國家/地區為中國的使用者，但已引起不少香港用戶的擔心。<br />\n<br />\n由於過去有小粉紅向政府投訴Playstation容許中國玩家切換到港服及台服，購買未經審查的遊戲，Sony因為壓力而關閉了Playstation中國商店。因此，令不少人擔心若果未來有任何人投訴香港的Playstation使用者違反國安法，Sony會同樣受壓而妥協。<br />\n<br />\n為釋除疑惑，本人作為PSN用戶也期望Sony及Playstation能夠回覆以下問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 因應香港的《國家安全法》，Sony未來會否將國安法相關條款應用於香港地區的使用者？<br />\n<br />\n2. 因應香港的《國家安全法》，用戶會否因為名字或聯天內容等觸犯相關條款，而被Sony停用戶口？<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果有使用者被指控違反國安法，Sony是否會為警方或政府提供用戶資料？<br />\n<br />\n4. 用戶使用Party或者PS Messages等文字或語音功能的聊天紀錄，會否提供予警察或政府作證據？<br />\n<br />\n敬候賜覆。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n<br />\n生意興隆<br />\n<br />\nPlaystation用戶 黃之鋒<br />\n<br />\n2020年10月15日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3427829233976227/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F3427829233976227%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=f4c33a48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3427829233976227/</a>"},{"pid":"3c436703e78d8052c46e6111d8d7e2ca3d3592bc","tid":2245601,"uid":294108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"一更新咗嗰吓真係嬲"},{"pid":"c40b4467676d2e5139d00f6590497f0927f23d73","tid":2245601,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T10:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789bed10b5e23ea7f82369618e3fc64cbe54c9be","tid":2245601,"uid":263534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"Gphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efcad7f3efe79853473948f3a12d11d785f9e14","tid":2245601,"uid":134781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"如果Bandai 跪低埋 gphone 咪冇得砌高達？"},{"pid":"97d261f9e538191b3faa2a37f0f75f3250f58f79","tid":2245601,"uid":32150,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9efcad7f3efe79853473948f3a12d11d785f9e14","tid":2245601,"uid":134781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"如果Bandai 跪低埋 gphone 咪冇得砌高達？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cc0e8c112f7bbd5953b52711fb4abad03a41cb","tid":2245601,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T17:51:36.000Z","msg":"太耐冇開機，原來已經咁撚屌<br />\n<br />\n之後都係不了"},{"pid":"1c724ffae457e60fa7a3cf8fba74dca5d17902e5","tid":2245601,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733dbdf68653caceaaba5342600fd95d3cbcb710","tid":2245601,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:25:13.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"615b34d1c1c3174294a422e9195cbed729d017ab","tid":2245601,"uid":54376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c